Package: foodmap
Title: Map Australia's Best Restaurants from Multiple Guides
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Peter", "Owen", email = "peter@bzi.com.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Scrapes restaurant guides (Broadsheet, Gourmet Traveller, Time Out,
    AGFG, Urban List, Good Food Guide), geocodes venues via the Google Places API,
    and exports KML files for import into Google My Maps.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3.9000
